description: Clara Moon: A Gateway to a World of Creativity, Mindfulness, and Artistic Expression! Pocket Corners Coloring Book brings you adorable cozy scenes tucked into the nooks and crannies of everyday life. From tiny bookshop hideaways to snug café corners, whimsical garden nooks, and dreamy bedroom spaces, each page is a delightful escape waiting for your colors. Key Features: + 40 Hand-Drawn Illustrations: Every design is carefully crafted to bring you joy and inspiration. + Portable Size: 8.5x8.5 inches. + Single-Sided Pages: Easy to color and make your artwork suitable for framing or gifting. + Suitable for All Skill Levels: Amazing for beginners and seasoned colorists alike. + Bringing Stress Relief: Immerse yourself in a calming environment, promoting relaxation and mindfulness.
